<section>
    <h2>About My Practice</h2>
    <p>Specialized in obstetrics and gynaecology, with experience in handling high risk pregnancies. I am committed to compassionate care and evidence-based practices, empowering women to embrace pregnancy as a natural and fulfilling experience.</p>
    <p>With a focus on holistic care, I provide comprehensive prenatal support, emphasizing natural childbirth methods and personalized birthing plans tailored to each patient’s values and preferences. I promote maternal health through evidence-based practices, fostering a supportive environment where expectant mothers feel informed and confident throughout their pregnancy and beyond.</p>
    <p>I have a strong focus on lactation support and postpartum care, ensuring seamless transitions into motherhood and providing comprehensive guidance to enhance breastfeeding success and maternal well-being.</p>
    <p>Furthermore, I provide compassionate care and education on a wide range of women’s health issues, encouraging proactive measures to achieve optimal physical and emotional health from adolescence through menopause, fostering a lasting commitment to self-care and wellness.</p>
</section>

